ASPHYXIA - Asphyxia [Unreleased] (2007)

Industrial / Electronica / Trance  / Harsh EBM / Dark Electro
   
"+ Album coming ! +" 

Marseille, 
France 
 
Asphyxia was born in August 2005, after some industrial/electronical tests on a music software. Throught this personal project I just put down my feelings, and Asphyxia is first made in order to evacuate sadness and hate, or other feeling I could have had since I started. Asphyxia music can be said as Electro-dark or Industrial, even if I try my best not to be a stereotype.

Band Members Romain Florentz, programming & voices
